nodes.text: Meet Wicket! is an article by Scott Chernoff that appeared in Star Wars Kids 6. It was based on "Wicket Unleashed", an article Chernoff wrote for Star Wars Insider 31. "Meet Wicket" contained information on the fictional character of Wicket Wystri Warrick, and an interview with Warwick Davis. It also featured an original illustration of Wicket by Chris Trevas.
